<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98946267755169></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98946267755169><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=12&mid=98946267755169>mathus majere</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, May 9th 10:44 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>i started as a human magician.  i soloed all the way up to 47 for the most part.  only on a few occasions did i group, mostly to break hell levels.  i can still solo blues at level 47.  only other classes i see soloing still are druids and necros for the most part.  also one advantage magicians have over wizards is that when traveling through mid to low level zones when something attacks you a wizard has to spend mana and then waste time medding to deal with the threat.  magicians don't.  a simple wave of the hand, pet command, and pet deals with it for you.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
